    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Let us instruct our children in the teachings of the word. If you will call, the Lord will answer you. He will say, Here I am; what would you have Me do for you? Heaven is linked with earth that every soul may be enabled to fulfill his mission. The Lord loves these children. He wants them brought up with an understanding of their high calling.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 31, 1909\" data-link=\"14074.9454001\">Manuscript 31, 1909</span>.</span></a></sup>",
    "puborder": 615,
