    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Human effort alone will not result in helping your children to perfect a character for heaven; but with divine help a grand and holy work may be accomplished.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">12<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"RH 10-25-1892\" data-link=\"821.12255\">The Review and Herald, October 25, 1892</span>.</span></a></sup>",
